modName: EyeCandy Staff of Magnus- Dual Sheath Redux Patch
summary: Dual Sheath Redux Patch For EyeCandy Staff of Magnus
descriptionHtml:
The original file is required and can be found at
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/41599/?]EyeCandy Staff of Magnus by Renegade1979[/url]

Also requires to function properly
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/34155/?]Dual Sheath Redux by Neovalen[/url]

I'm aware that the author of the original file has been banned and I could not contact them. I however did ask mods and staff several times about policy of posting this file. I have never received an answer on it.

Base mesh used is from [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/41599/?]EyeCandy Staff of Magnus by Renegade1979[/url]
. User was banned so I could not contact them for permission . I will remove this immediatly if asked by a mod or staff regarding policy.
The meshes included in this mod are of my own (miniscule) work upon the base mesh included from the original file. That mesh is highly required for this to work at all .
author: Stalfos81
